N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4002.19 - Financial responsibility

State Regulations

Any participant who shall accumulate unpaid
obligations, default in obligations, issue drafts or checks that are dishonored
or payment refused, or otherwise display financial irresponsibility reflecting
on his or her experience, character or general fitness, shall be subject to
refusal, suspension or revocation of license. Notes
